.git
.gitignore
.github

# Secrets — must never end up in an image layer
.env
.env.*
*.pem
*.key

# Per-user orchestrator privkeys + DNA analytics annotations live under
# backend/data/. Both are LOCAL state — copying them into a Docker image
# would (1) leak production user privkeys across containers, (2) baseline
# every redeployed container with stale DNA feedback that doesn't belong
# to it. The container should mount its own volume here at runtime.
backend/data
**/backend/data
data/orchestrator-wallets.json

# Local node modules / build outputs
node_modules
**/node_modules
.next
**/.next
dist
**/dist
coverage
**/coverage
tsconfig.tsbuildinfo
**/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo

# Runtime artefacts
logs
**/logs
artifacts
**/artifacts
postgres-data

# Tooling / editor
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo

# Docs / design notes — never ship markdown into containers
*.md
!frontend/README.md
.design-handoff
.claude
